TODAY'S TOP STORIES: 

NBSK price barely flickers on FOEX index 

BRUSSELS, Nov. 27, 2001 - The pace of change of pulp 
prices has slowed down according to Finland's FOEX 
price indexes. 
<http://cm.paperloop.com/redirect.jsp?cmID=C1493085L7978U62309>

